The hidden one is acquired!

455
00:28:53,300 --> 00:28:54,970
The one who revolts is captured!

456
00:28:54,970 --> 00:28:56,930
In the streets of Mumbai,

457
00:28:56,970 --> 00:28:59,010
With fright they will say 'Salute'!

